.%20There%20was%20no%20moment%20of%20clarity%20or%20significant%20occurrence%2C%20just%20a%20realization%20that%20my%20daily%20actions%20were%20harmful%20to%20the%20earth.%20I%20committed%20to%20small%20changes%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20and%20my%20journey%20took%20off%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20I%20removed%20myself%20from%20capitalism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20teenage%20man%20throwing%20money%20int%20he%20air.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581664dcefc010bea24cdec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22748%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreenfield%20in%202009%20as%20a%20young%20college%20student.%3Cp%3ERobin%20Greenfield%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20break%20free%20from%20capitalism.%20Before%20starting%20this%20journey%2C%20I%20owned%20my%20own%20marketing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20I%20started%20removing%20myself%20from%20the%20monetary%20system.%20I%20started%20pulling%20away%20from%20my%20company%2C%20destroyed%20my%20credit%20cards%20and%20closed%20my%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20only%20use%20cash%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20bank%20account.%20If%20it%20is%20stolen%2C%20it's%20gone.%20I%20will%20never%20own%20a%20house%20or%20rent%20an%20apartment%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20need%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETiny%20living%20helps%20me%20connect%20to%20nature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robin%20Greenfield%20in%20a%20tiny%20structure%20in%20North%20Carolina%20forest.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581a3d0cefc010bea24d8fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreenfield%20stands%20outside%20his%20off-grid%20tiny%20structure%20near%20Asheville%2C%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Tew%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20tiny%20helps%20me%20enjoy%20my%20life.%20Most%20of%20us%20live%20in%20far%20larger%20spaces%20than%20we%20need.%20The%20more%20stuff%20I%20had%2C%20the%20more%20time%20I%20spent%20taking%20care%20of%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20focus%20became%20living%20in%20harmony%20with%20plants%20and%20animals.%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20living%20in%20small%2C%20off-grid%20shelters%20I%20either%20built%20or%20purchased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stay%20on%20land%20in%20people's%20gardens%20in%20exchange%20for%20helping%20the%20owners%20live%20more%20sustainably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20first%20tiny%20house%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20as%20a%20marketer%20completely%20and%20moved%20into%20a%2050-square-foot%20home%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0so%20small%20that%20I%20couldn't%20even%20stand%20up%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20living%20in%20San%20Diego%20and%20was%20searching%20on%20Facebook%20listings%20for%20a%20camper%20van%20to%20live%20in%20while%20I%20built%20my%20first%20tiny%20house.%20I%20found%20this%20small%20shed-like%20building%20listed%20for%20%24950.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20typo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20clicked%20on%20it%20and%20saw%20it%20was%20a%20wooden%20box%20on%20a%20trailer%20and%20priced%20correctly.%20I%20bought%20it%20and%20put%20a%20callout%20on%20Craigslist%20and%20to%20my%205%2C000%20Facebook%20friends%3A%20%26quot%3BHello%20community%2C%20I'm%20looking%20for%20someone%20who%20has%20an%20unused%20backyard%20and%20would%20benefit%20from%20hosting%20me%20and%20my%20tiny%20house.%20In%20return%2C%20I%20can%20help%20you%20transition%20to%20a%20more%20sustainable%20life.%26quot%3B%20Jim%20responded%20and%20I%20lived%20in%20his%20backyard%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trailer%20had%20a%20composting%20toilet%2C%20rainwater%20shower%2C%20and%20no%20electricity.%20When%20I%20moved%20away%2C%20I%20auctioned%20the%20trailer%20and%20donated%20the%20proceeds%20to%20a