0other%20employees%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECushman%20helps%20landlords%20fill%20their%20spaces%2C%20from%20office%20buildings%20to%20retail%20stores%20to%20warehouses%2C%20and%20aids%20companies%20in%20finding%20space%20to%20lease.%20Cushman%2C%20Companieh%20said%2C%20ensures%20both%20real-estate%20investors%20and%20tenants%20can%20use%20an%20%26quot%3Baggregation%20of%20the%20best%20market%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20foot%20traffic%2C%20drive%20time%2C%20and%20weather%2C%20to%20find%20the%20best%20space%20for%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20that%2C%20Companieh%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Cushman%20employees%20work%20directly%20at%20client%20sites.%20If%20they're%20managing%20a%20big%20office%20building%2C%20for%20example%2C%20they'll%20work%20out%20of%20that%20building%20rather%20than%20a%20Cushman%20office.%20The%20building%20landlord%20or%20a%20tenant%20company%20may%20fire%20questions%20at%20the%20Cushman%20manager%20%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20onboard%20an%20employee%2C%20for%20example.%20Cushman%20uses%20AI%20chatbots%20to%20supplement%20its%20other%20offerings%20for%20client%20support%20to%20solve%20their%20problems%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%2C%20Companieh%20said%2C%20can%20help%20Cushman%20employees%20%26quot%3Bmaximize%20their%20time%20to%20best%20serve%20the%20client.%26quot%3B%20It's%20exciting%20to%20introduce%20transformative%20technology%20in%20a%20field%20where%20change%20is%20so%20often%20gradual%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20that%20excites%20me%20most%20is%20human%20behavior%20change%20and%20getting%20colleagues%20that%20would%20have%20never%20thought%20about%20doing%20things%20differently%20to%20not%20only%20understand%20it%20but%20also%20be%20empowered%20by%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Companieh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanieh%20said%20clients%2C%20including%20landlords%20and%20tenant%20companies%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong