%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fries%2C%20dubbed%20British%20Fries%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20looked%20exactly%20like%20the%20crispy%20salted%20fries%20served%20at%20McDonald's.%20They%20were%20even%20tucked%20in%20red-colored%20sleeve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grabbed%20a%20few%20of%20the%20hot-to-the-touch%20fries%20and%20shoved%20a%20couple%20in%20my%20mouth.%20I%20was%20instantly%20impressed.%20They%20were%20addictive%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20restrain%20myself%20from%20gobbling%20up%20the%20whole%20sleeve%20of%20fries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20next%20item%20I%20tried%20was%20the%20Not%20a%20Chicken%20Sandwich.%20It%20was%20not%20so%20great.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mr.Charlie's%20Not%20So%20Chicken%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657345a07a3c8094d5db0799%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Not%20So%20Chicken%20sandwich%20came%20with%20a%20mushy%20bun%20that%20easily%20cracked.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fake%20chicken%20patty%20was%20not%20uniform.%20It%20didn't%20come%20close%20to%20looking%20like%20a%20fried%20chicken%20breast.%20But%20getting%20the%20look%20and%20texture%20right%20for%20plant-based%20chicken%20is%20a%20hard%20thing%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr.Charlie's%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fplant-based-chicken-burger-singapore-tindle-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiNDLE%20Chicken%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20chicken%20products%2C%20rather%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Freview-new-beyond-fried-chicken-nuggets-kfc-plant-based-meat-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeyond%20Meat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20plant-based%20chicken%20products%20have%20been%20tested%20by%20many%20fast-food%20chains%20like%20Panda%20Express%20and%20KFC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20bite%2C%20the%20sandwich%20ta