%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMr.%20Charlie's%20Not%20a%20Cheeseburger%20came%20really%20close%20in%20presentation%20to%20looking%20like%20a%20McDonald's%20cheeseburger.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20plant-based%20chicken%20sandwich%2C%20the%20Impossible%20Foods%20alt-meat%20patty%20gives%20Mr.Charlie's%20burgers%20an%20authentic%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20you%20might%20think%20you're%20biting%20into%20a%20real%20beef%20burger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Impossible%20patty%20looks%20like%20ground%20beef.%20This%20sandwich%20was%20layered%20with%20chopped%20onions%20and%20a%20mix%20of%20mustard%20and%20ketchup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr.Charlie's%20uses%20dairy-free%20cheese%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffollowyourheart.com%2Fproduct_category%2Fdairy-free-cheese%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFollow%20Your%20Heart%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20looked%20like%20cheese%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20taste%20anything%20like%20cheese.%20It%20didn't%20offend%20me%20like%20the%20plant-based%20chicken%20nugget%2C%20which%20had%20a%20foul%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vegan%20cheese%20was%20flavorless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20try%20one%20of%20Mr.Charlie's%20burgers%2C%20I'd%20suggest%20saving%20a%20buck%20by%20ordering%20a%20sandwich%20without%20cheese.%20The%20Not%20a%20Cheeseburger%20cost%20%247.99%20a%20la%20carte%2C%20while%20the%20Not%20a%20Hamburger%20cost%20%246.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20BigChuck%20is%20clearly%20the%20hero%20of%20the%20menu.%20And%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20Big%20Mac.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mr.Charlie's%20BigChuck%20burger%20looks%20like%20a%20Big%20Mac%20from%20McDonald's.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657349497a3c8094d5db0abb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMr.Charlie's%