%20crossing%20all%20limits.%20They%20are%20repeatedly%20insulting%20people%20on%20constitutional%20posts.%20They%20have%20been%20insulting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%2020%20years%20because%20he%20comes%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20and%20the%20OBC%20community.%20They%20insulted%20the%20President%20because%20she%20is%20a%20tribal%20woman.%20You%20are%20a%20farmer's%20son.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20someone%20from%20the%20Jat%20community%20became%20Vice-President.%20They%20have%20insulted%20this%20post.%20We%20are%20making%20it%20clear%2C%20we%20will%20not%20tolerate%20the%20insult%20of%20the%20Vice-President%20and%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Joshi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20your%20honour%20and%20to%20protest%20against%20them%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20and%20participate%20in%20the%20question%20and%20answer%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20mimicking%20the%20Vice-President%20on%20Parliament%20premises%20has%20raised%20a%20political%20storm.%20Mr%20Banerjee%20is%20among%20the%20141%20Opposition%20MPs%20suspended%20for%20demanding%20a%20statement%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20last%20week.%20Yesterday%2C%20while%20protesting%20near%20Makar%20Dwar%20to%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%2C%20the%20Serampore%20MP%20started%20mimicking%20the%20Vice-President.%20Other%20MPs%20were%20seen%20laughing%20as%20Mr%20Banerjee%20imitated%20Mr%20Dhankhar's%20gestures.%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20seen%20filming%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20he%20had%20seen%20the%20video%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20pained%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Addressing%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BImagine%20what%20I%20felt%20when%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20your%20party%2C%20an%20MP%2C%20was%20filming%20an%20act%20making%20fun%20of%20me%2C%20a%20personal%20attack.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20the%20insult%20of%20a%20farmer%20or%20a%20community%2C%20it's%20disrespect%20to%20the%20post%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman.%20And%20that%20too%20by%20a%20party%20that%20ruled%20the%20country%20for%20so%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20official%20Instagram%20handle%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20posted%20the%20video%2C%20but%20later%20took%20it%20down.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20shameful.%20You%20used%20an%20official%20handle%20to%20humiliate%20me%20for%20my%20farmer%20background%2C%20to%20humiliate%20me%20as%20a%20Jat%2C%20to%20humiliate%20my%20position.%20This%20is%20very%20serious%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20under%20fire%20for%20the%20unprecedented%20suspension%20spree%20of%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20used%20the%20mimicry%20video%20to%20hit%20back.%C2%A0Union%20ministers%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20and%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20and%20the%20party's%20official%20X%20handle%2C%20termed%20Mr%20Banerjee's%20mimicry%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontemptible%20act%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20country%20was%20wondering%20why%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20suspended%2C%20here%20is%20the%20reason...%20TMC%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20mocked%20Honourable%20Vice%20President%2C%20while%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20lustily%20cheered%20him%20on.%20One%20can%20imagine%20how%20reckless%20and%20violative%20they%20have%20been%20of%20the%20House!%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP's%20official%20handle%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20video%20showing%20Mr%20Gandhi%20recording%20Mr%20Banerjee's%20mimicry%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20posted%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20record%20-%20Congress%20supports%20those%20who%20RIDICULE%20a%20constitutional%20position!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703064780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fg4vbtl0g_bjp-mp