0moved%20Delhi's%20Patiala%20House%20Court%20and%20sought%20direction%20from%20the%20Economic%20Offence%20Wing%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20Superintendent%20of%20Mandoli%20Jail%2C%20where%20conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekhar%20is%20in%20judicial%20custody%2C%20to%20immediately%20restrain%20him%20from%20issuing%20any%20further%20letters%2C%20messages%2C%20or%20statements%20addressed%20to%20her%20directly%20or%20indirectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJacqueline%20in%20her%20plea%20alleged%20that%20Chandrashekhar%20persistently%20engages%20in%20the%20unsolicited%20dissemination%20of%20troubling%20letters%20to%20numerous%20electronic%20and%20print%20media%20platforms.%20These%20letters%2C%20once%20published%20by%20the%20media%20outlets%2C%20create%20an%20alarming%20and%20distressing%20environment%20for%20her%2C%20the%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20widespread%20publication%20amplifies%20the%20intimidation%20and%20harassment%2C%20profoundly%20affecting%20the%20applicant's%20safety%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjacqueline-fernandez-asks-court-to-drop-case-against-her-by-probe-agency-4699035%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%7C%C2%A0Jacqueline%20Fernandez%20Asks%20Court%20To%20Drop%20Case%20Against%20Her%20By%20Probe%20Agency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actress%20Jacqueline%20is%20a%20protected%20witness%20in%20the%20FIR%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Economic%20Offence%20Wing%20(EOW)%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Rs%20200%20crore%20money-laundering%20and%20extortion%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekhar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEOW%20in%20its%20reply%20supports%20Jacqueline%20Fernandez's%20application%20and%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20observed%20that%20the%20accused%20Sukash%20Chandershekhar%20has%20also%20been%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20sending%20letters%2C%20concerning%20the%20present%20applicant%2C%20to%20media%20platforms%2C%20through%20various%20means%2C%20which%20is%20not%20only%20harassing%2F%20threatening%20the%20present%20applicant%20directly%20but%20also%20affecting%20her%20social%2F%20professional%20assignments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20such%20an%20aggravating%20nature%20of%20the%20threat%2Fharassment%20to%20the%20victim%2Fapplicant%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern%20for%20the%20investigating%20agency%20that%20an%20important%20witness%20of%20the%20case%20is%20being%20coerced%2Fharassed%2F%20threatened%20by%20the%20accused%2C%20as%20it%20will%20have%20serious%20implications%20on%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20trial%20of%20the%20case%2C%20concerning%20the%20present%20applicant%2Fwitness%2C%20stated%20EOW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJacqueline%20in%20her%20plea%20stated%20that%20she%20has%20no%20previous%20interaction%20with%20the%20accused%20Sukash%20Chandershekhar%20and%20her%20interaction%20with%20him%20started%20only%20during%20the%20period%20of%20commission%20of%20crime%20by%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20present%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20an%20important%20witness%20in%20the%20present%20case%20to%20prove%20the%20prosecution%20version%2C%20said%20EOW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20the%20submissions%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20judge%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20January%2017%2C%202023%2C%20for%20further%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJacqueline%20Fernandez%20has%20recently%20also%20moved%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20seeking%20the%20quashing%20of%20ECIR%20(FIR)%20and%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20Rs%20200%20Crore%20money%20laundering%20case%20involving%20alleged%20conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJacqueline%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20has%20acted%20in%20a%20partisan%20manner%20while%20arraigning%20her%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20Impugned%20Complaint.%20The%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20has%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20Nora%20Fatehi%20despite%20it%20being%20an%20admitted%20fact%20on%20record%20that%20her%20family%20member%20received%20a%20BMW%20car%20from%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekhar%20on%20her%20instructions%2C%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20is%20playing%20hot%20and%20cold%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20In%20identical%20facts%2C%20she%20has%20been%20arraigned%20as%20an%20accused%2C%20Aditi%20Singh%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Original%20Complainant%2C%20and%20artists%20like%20Nora%20Fatehi%20and%20other%20artists%20like%20Nikita%20Tamboli%2C%20Chahatt%20Khanna%2C%20and%20Sophyia%20Singh%20who%20physically%20visited%20the%20Tihar%20Jail%20premises%20have%20not%20been%20arraigned%20as%20an%20accused.%20This%20reflects%20a%20malafide%20investigation%20against%20her%2C%20Jacqueline%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20case%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20hinges%20on%20a%20single%20alleged%20news%20article%20shared%20with%20Jacqueline.%20Based%20on%20this%20sole%20piece%20of%20evidence%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20contends%20that%20she%20might%20have%20been%20aware%20of%20Sukesh's%20imprisonment%20but%20still%20chose%20to%20accept%20gifts%20from%20him%2C%20thereby%20she%20has%20been%20arraigned%20as%20an%20accused%20for%20the%20offence%20of%20money%20laundering%2C%20the%20plea%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJacqueline%20Fernandez%20is%20a%20Sri%20Lankan%20National%20living%20in%20India%20since%202009%20and%20belongs%20to%20a%20Bollywood%20fraternity%20and%20holds%20a%20good%20name%20in%20the%20Bollywood%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20case%20is%20based%20on%20an%20FIR%20filed%20by%20Delhi%20Police's%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20(EOW)%20against%20Sukesh%20Chandrasekhar%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20cheating%20and%20extorting%20Aditi%20Singh%2C%20wife%20of%20former%20promoter%20of%20Religare%20Enterprises%20Shivinder%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20October%202019%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%20at%20Religare%20Finvest%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrasekhar%20and%20his%20associates%20reportedly%20took%20money%20from%20Aditi%20after%20posing%20as%20government%20officials%20and%20promising%20to%20get%20bail%20for%20her%20husband.%20Chandrasekhar%20reportedly%20persuaded%20Aditi%20to%20transfer%20money%20by%20impersonating%20a%20central%20government%20official%20over%20a%20spoof%20call%20while%20he%20was%20lodged%20in%20Rohini%20jail%20and%20promised%20to%20manage%20bail%20for%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20his%20actor%20wife%20Leena%20Maria%20Paul%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20September%20last%20year%20for%20their%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20duping%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703063640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fmnrucq0g_jacqueline-fernandez-_625x300_02_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjacqueline-fernandez-moves-court-over-conman-sukesh-chandrasekhars-letters-4708824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bollywood%20Actor%20Jacqueline%20Fernandez%20on%20Wednesday%20moved%20Delhi's%20Patiala%20House%20Court%20and%20sought%20direction%20from%20the%20Economic%20Offence%20Wing%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20Superintendent%20of%20Mandoli%20Jail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjacqueline-fernandez-moves-court-over-conman-sukesh-chandrasekhars-letters-4708824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjacqueline-fernandez-moves-court-over-conman-sukesh-chandrasekhars-