%20the%20side%20to%20avoid%20being%20hit%20by%20the%20men%20who%20are%20busy%20attacking%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20passengers%20try%20to%20calm%20them%20down%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%20Both%20the%20men%20are%20seen%20throwing%20punches%20at%20each%20other%20and%20none%20of%20them%20stops%20before%20the%20short%20clip%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20been%20viewed%20close%20to%202%2C000%20times%20and%20amassed%20reactions%20from%20several%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20educated%20and%20live%20in%20the%20capital%20of%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BPunches%20are%20so%20Professional...%20it's%20Mohammad%20Ali%20vs%20George%20Chuvalo%20level%20of%20boxing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20diamonds%20and%20both%20must%20be%20sent%20to%20Olympics%20games%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20third%20user%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20video%20had%20surfaced%20in%20June%20too%20that%20showed%20two%20backpack-wearing%20men%20engaged%20in%20an%20ugly%20fight%20inside%20a%20crowded%20Delhi%20Metro%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20were%20also%20seen%20punching%20and%20trying%20to%20push%20each%20other%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMRC%20had%20reacted%20to%20the%20video%2C%20issuing%20a%20statement%20in%20which%20it%20urged%20commuters%20to%20%26quot%3Bconduct%20themselves%20responsibly%26quot%3B%20while%20travelling%20in%20the%20Metro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20also%20said%20that%20flying%20squads%20regularly%20monitor%20such%20behaviour%20and%20warned%20of%20action%20against%20unruly%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703063400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fjjn7bfe8_delhi-metro-fight_625x300_20_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fpunches-are-so-professional-video-of-fight-inside-delhi-metro-is-viral-4708930%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20passengers%20t