2C%20while%20it%20remains%20silent%20on%20the%20real%20issue%20of%20why%20and%20how%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Mysuru%20facilitated%20entry%20of%20two%20intruders%20into%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2013th%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20now%20charged%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1737356889111839181%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bidhuri%20is%20facing%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20privileges%20committee%20for%20his%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20Mr%20Ali.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20two%20MPs%20appeared%20before%20the%20panel.%20Mr%20Ali%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20BJP%20members%20of%20making%20a%20derogatory%20remark%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20had%20expressed%20regret%20over%20Mr%20Bidhuri's%20remarks%20and%20these%20were%20expunged%20from%20the%20proceedings.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20Mr%20Bidhuri%2C%20too%2C%20had%20regretted%20his%20comments%20in%20his%20meeting%20with%20the%20privileges%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ali%2C%20who%20is%20among%20the%20suspended%20MPs%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20new%20definition%20of%20New%20India%20is%20that%20those%20using%20slangs%20will%20sit%20inside%20Parliament%20and%20those%20asking%20question%20will%20be%20outside.%20%26quot%3BThe%20decorum%20of%20the%20House%20is%20not%20disrupted%20when%20questions%20are%20asked.%20It%20is%20disrupted%20when%20a%20BJP%20MP%20uses%20slangs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Ali%2C%20who%20has%20been%20suspended%20by%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20for%20alleged%20anti-party%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ali%20asked%20why%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20Mr%20Simha%20yet.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%20to%20crucify%20those%20asking%20questions%20to%20the%20government.%20I%20was%20not%20even%20present%20in%20the%20session%20and%20they%20added%20my%20name%20to%20the%20suspension%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaugata%20Ray%2C%20MP%20from%20Congress's%20INDIA%20bloc%20ally%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20said%20the%20mass%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20was%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20democracy%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20shouldn't%20have%20been%20done.%20We%20were%20demanding%20the%20suspension%20of%20BJP%20MP%20(Pratap%20Simha)%2C%20but%20they%20instead%20suspended%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Mr%20Simha%20has%20told%20the%20Speaker%20that%20the%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20intruders%2C%20Manoranjan%20D%2C%20was%20from%20his%20constituency%20and%20had%20asked%20for%20a%20visitor's%20pass%20to%20visit%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703059200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F0mlnu7h8_ramesh-bidhuri-pratap-simha-split_625x300_20_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-jairam-ramesh-ramesh-bidhuri-pratap-simha-amid-suspension-spree-opposition-asks-why-no-action-against-two-bjp-mps-4708565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20the%20suspension%20spree%20of%20MPs%20over%20their%20conduct%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20questioned%20why%20two%20BJP%20members%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20have%20not%20faced%20any%20action%20yet%20despite%20being%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20huge%20controversies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-jairam-ramesh-ramesh-bidhuri-pratap-simha-amid-suspension-spree-opposition-asks-why-no-action-against-two-bjp-mps-4708565%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-jairam-ramesh-ramesh-bidhuri-pratap-simha-amid-suspension-spree-opposition-asks-why-no-action-against-two-bjp-mps-4708565%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-jairam-ramesh-ramesh-bidhuri-pratap-simha-amid-suspension-spree-opposition-asks-why-no-action-against-two-bjp-mps-4708565%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress's%20'Donate%20for%20Desh'%20Recalls%20the%20Discomfort%20with%20Corporate%20Funding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20132158%2FScreenshot-2023-12-20-at-1.20.41.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%202019%20book%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBusiness%20and%20Politics%20in%20India%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Christophe%20Jaffrelot%20said%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20be%20anointed%20by%20the%20corporates.%20He%20argued%20that%20there%20are%20unmistakable%20linkages%20between%20the%20corporates%20which%20determine%20politics%20and%20the%20high%20political%20positions%20the%20ruling%20party%20leaders%20get%20in%20the%20structure%20of%20governance.%20In%20contrast%20to%20corporate-driven%20funding%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20launched%20its%20Donate%20for%20Desh%20online%20crowdfunding%20drive%20to%20engage%20in%20the%202024%20electoral%20process.%20It%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20donate%20Rs%20138%20or%20its%20multiples%20to%20the%20party%20in%20a%20transparent%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETilak%20Swaraj%20Fund%20and%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20the%20early%201920s%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20such%20methods%20were%20adopted%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20were%20recommended%20in%20the%201964%20report%20of%20the%20Santhanam%20Committee%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20to%20fight%20corruption.%20In%201920-21%2C%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20Lokmanya%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%2C%20the%20Tilak%20Swaraj%20Fund%20was%20set%20up%20with%20the%20challenging%20goal%20of%20collecting%20Rs%201%20crore%20from%20people%20to%20achieve%20swaraj%20or%20independence%20in%20one%20year.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20travelled%20across%20India%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people.%20It%20was%20to%20be%20a%20tribute%20to%20Lokmanya%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%2C%20who%20electrified%20the%20nation%20with%20his%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9CSwaraj%20is%20my%20birth%20right%20and%20I%20shall%20have%20it.%E2%80%9D%20The%20present%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20people%20very%20similarly.%20While%20vigorously%20campaigning%20for%20funds%20for%20the%20Tilak%20Swaraj%20Fund%2C%20Gandhi%20found%20that%20large%20numbers%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20downtrodden%20paid%20small%20sums%2C%20worth%20less%20than%2025%20paise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20characteristic%20brilliance%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20transparency%20and%20honesty%20associated%20with%20the%20collection%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20its%20utilisation%20would%20define%20patriotism%20and%20display%20probity%20and%20integrity%20in%20expending%20public%20money.%20That%20observation%20about%20money%20is%20so%20intensely%20relevant%20for%20our%20time%2C%20when%20anonymous%20electoral%20bonds%20introduced%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20have%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20massive%20collections%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20without%20disclosing%20the%20sources%20of%20such%20funding%20and%20its%20utilisation.%20The%20online%20crowdfunding%20campaign%20sounds%20so%20refreshing%20because%20it%20draws%20inspiration%20from%20the%20method%20adopted%20for%20mobilising%20resources%20for%20the%20Tilak%20Swaraj%20Fund%20in%20the%20early%201920s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EObservations%20of%20Santhanam%20Committee%20in%201964%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Donate%20for%20Desh%20campaign%20is%20also%20evocative%20of%20one%20of%20the%20key%20observations%20of%20the%20Santhanam%20Committee%20Report%20of%201964%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20to%20prevent%20corruption.%20It%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20public%20belief%20in%20the%20prevalence%20of%20corruption%20at%20high%20political%20levels%20has%20been%20strengthened%20by%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20funds%20are%20collected%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20time%20of%20elections.%E2%80%9D%20It%20very%20sharply%20observed%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20suspicions%20attach%20not%20only%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20but%20to%20all%20parties%2C%20as%20often%20the%20Opposition%20can%20also%20support%20private%20vested%20interests%20as%20well%20as%20members%20of%20the%20government%20party.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Committee%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cessential%20that%20the%20conduct%20of%20political%20parties%20should%20be%20regulated%20in%20this%20matter%20by%20strict%20principles%20in%20relation%20to%20collection%20of%20funds%20and%20electioneering.%E2%80%9D%20Acknowledging%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20parties%20cannot%20be%20run%20and%20elections%20cannot%20be%20fought%20without%20large%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20stressed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthese%20funds%20should%20come%20openly%20from%20the%20supporters%20or%20sympathisers%20of%20the%20parties%20concerned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20Santhanam%20Committee%20very%20sensitively%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20even%20one%20family%20in%20three%20pays%20one%20rupee%20a%20year%20to%20a%20political%20party%2C%20the%20total%20annual%20contribution%20will%20be%20more%20than%20what%20is%20needed%20for%20all%20legitimate%20purposes%20of%20all%20political%20parties%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20While%20regretting%20that%20political%20parties%20were%20unwilling%20to%20make%20small%20collections%20on%20a%20wide%20basis%20and%20resorted%20to%20shortcuts%20through%20large%20donations%2C%20the%20Committee%20asserted%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutes%20the%20major%20source%20of%20corruption%20and%20even%20more%20of%20suspicion%20of%20corruption%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20juxtaposing%20the%20Donate%20for%20Desh%20campaign%20of%20the%20Congress%20with%20the%20campaign%20for%20the%20Tilak%20Swaraj%20Fund%20of%201920s%20and%20the%20invaluable%20observations%20of%20Santhanam%20Committee%20of%201964%2C%20a%20clear%20lesson%20is%20learnt%3A%20to%20appreciate%20the%20point%20that%20to%20rid%20public%20life%20of%20corruption%2C%20the%20non-transparent%20method%20of%20collection%20of%20money%20through%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20must%20be%20dispensed%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAffinity%20of%20people%20with%20political%20party%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20reaching%20out%20to%20people%20for%20donating%20money%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20party%20has%20set%20an%20example%2C%20remaining%20rooted%20in%20the%20larger%20collective%20life%20and%20democratic%20space%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20which%20remain%20%E2%80%9CWe%20the%20People%E2%80%9D%20or%20in%20the%20poetic%20words%20of%20Tagore%20%E2%80%9CJana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%9D%20who%20ascribed%20them%20the%20status%20of%20%E2%80%9CAdhinayak%E2%80%9D%20in%20our%20national%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20launched%20by%20the%20Congress%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20was%20suggested%20to%20those%20spearheading%20it%20to%20appeal%20to%20people%20to%20donate%20the%20very%20modest%20sum%20of%20Rs%2010%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20party.%20It%20was%20an%20eminently%20doable%20proposition%20which%20vast%20millions%20would%20have%20happily%20accepted.%20The%20spirit%20embodied%20in%20such%20methods%20are%20reflected%20in%20the%20Donate%20for%20Desh%20campaign%2C%20which%20constitutes%20a%20refreshing%20method%20of%20ridding%20the%20politics%20and%20political%20and%20electoral%20process%20of%20money%20from%20corporates%2C%20who%20often%20shape%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20regimes%20to%20which%20they%20contribute%20huge%20sums.%20The%20tag%20of%20crony%20capitalism%20is%20now%20defining%20the%20current%20political%20regime%20at%20the%20Centre.%20It%20represents%20a%20huge%20challenge%2C%20and%20the%20method%20adopted%20by%20Congress%20constitutes%20a%20small%20but%20decisive%20step%20in%20this%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20%3Cspan%3ESahu%3C%2Fspan%3E%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%2C%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703058820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20132158%2FScreenshot-2023-12-20-at-1.20.41.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongresss-donate-for-desh-recalls-the-discomfort-with-corporate-funding%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20also%20evocative%20of%20one%20of%20the%20key%20observations%20of%20the%20Santhanam%20Committee%20Report%20of%201964%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20to%20prevent%20corruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongresss-donate-for-desh-recalls-the-discomfort-with-corporate-funding%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NHAI%20to%20start%20rolling%20out%20sat-based%20tolling%20on%20NHs%20soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703058631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106148520%2Cimgsize-67982.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fgreat-news-nhai-to-start-rolling-out-satellite-ba