st%20is%20outright%20saying%20the%20central%20bank%20is%20a%20poor%20communicator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20point%20of%20Fed%20communication%20is%20to%20do%20two%20things%3A%20One%20is%20to%20be%20transparent%2C%20and%20two%20is%20to%20enhance%20the%20power%20of%20forward%20policy%20guidance.%20Instead%2C%20Fed%20communication%20confuses%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-19%2Fel-erian-says-fed-has-a-real-problem-with-communication%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMohamed%20El-Erian%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Bloomberg%20Television%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20have%20a%20real%20problem%20with%20Fed%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20El-Erian%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Queens'%20College%2C%20Cambridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEl-Erian's%20comments%20came%20after%20the%20Fed%20last%20Wednesday%20kept%20interest%20rates%20steady%20for%20the%20third%20straight%20time%20and%20signaled%20three%20rate%20cuts%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20sending%20financial%20markets%20on%20a%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20market%20participants%20are%20even%20pricing%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-2024-outlook-us-economy-unemployment-inflation-recession-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esteeper-than-expected%20rate%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20anticipation%20of%20a%20weaker%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20Fed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell's%20press%20conference%20last%20week%2C%20several%20Fed%20officials%20said%20that%20expectations%20of%20a%20rate%20cut%20early%20next%20year%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-15%2Ffed-s-williams-says-talk-of-march-rate-cut-is-premature%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremature%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20too%20dovish%20ahead%20of%20inflation%20data%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEl-Erian%20told%20Bloomberg%20such%20contrad