businessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fagri-business%2Finspector-raj-re-emerges-as-centres-wheat-stockholding-limit-order-turns-ammunition-against-processors%2Farticle67655086.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20on%20December%208%20tightened%20the%20stocking%20norms%20for%20retailers%2C%20wholesalers%2C%20and%20processors.%20According%20to%20these%20norms%2C%20any%20retail%20outlet%2C%20including%20big%20chains%20at%20the%20retail%20outlet%20level%2C%20can%20stock%20up%20to%20five%20tonnes%20of%20wheat%20limit%2C%20as%20against%20the%20earlier%2010-tonne%20ceiling.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20traders%20and%20wholesalers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20big%20chain%20retailers%20at%20depot%20level%2C%20the%20limit%20has%20been%20cut%20from%202%2C000%20tonnes%20to%201%2C000%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20in%20the%20case%20of%20processors%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eatta%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eand%20other%20flour%20products%20like%3Ci%3E%C2%A0sooji%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eand%C2%A0%3Ci%3Emaida%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20maximum%20capacity%20will%20be%2070%25%20of%20the%20monthly%20installed%20capacity%20of%20the%20mills%20multiplied%20by%20four%2C%20which%20is%20the%20remaining%20months%20of%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20food%20ministry%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20all%20stakeholders%20involved%20to%20adhere%20to%20their%20respective%20stocking%20limits%20by%20January%206%2C%202024%2C%20in%20case%20the%20stocks%20held%20by%20them%20are%20higher%20than%20the%20restricted%20limits.%20Additionally%2C%20wheat%20stocking%20entities%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20register%20themselves%20on%20the%20wheat%20stock%20limit%20portal%20and%20update%20the%20stock%20position%20every%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20speculation%20that%20the%20government%20may%20ease%20existing%20norms%20depending%20on%20the%20reduction%20in%20supplies%20available%20in%20the%20market%20eventually%20with%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20season%20in%20April.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20easing%20of%20norms%20may%20first%20benefit%20processors%20from%20February%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20stock%20more%20as%20produce%20from%20the%20new%20crop%20starts%20arriving%20in%20the%20market%20from%20mid-February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20relaxation%20in%20norms%20may%20come%20later%2C%20those%20affected%20by%20inspections%20suggest%20authorities%20concerned%20first%20gather%20inputs%20and%20then%20send%20officials%20for%20inspection.%20Some%20of%20the%20mill%20owners%20and%20traders%20are%20said%20to%20have%20conveyed%20the%20same%20to%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703054126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19161235%2F31764443254_73b92a3ef0_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwheat-traders-processors-upset-over-frequent-inspections-for-enforcing-stocking-norms-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20on%20December%208%20tightened%20the%20stocking%20norms%20for%20wheat%20retailers%2C%20wholesalers%2C%20and%20processors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwheat-traders-processors-upset-over-frequent-inspections-for-enforcing-stocking-norms-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKey%20Emoji%20Means%20Cocaine%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20Drugs%20Are%20Sold%20In%20Online%20Gaming%20Chatrooms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENarcotics%20police%20the%20world%20over%20are%20sprucing%20up%20their%20video%20game%20skills%2C%20as%20cartels%20go%20increasingly%20online%20to%20sell%20drugs%20and%20recruit%20dealers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCartels%20have%20been%20incredibly%20tech%20savvy%20over%20recent%20years%2C%20reaching%20vast%20audiences%2C%26quot%3B%20Benjamin%20Shultz%2C%20foreign%20malign%20influence%20analyst%20at%20Deloitte%2C%20told%20a%20Council%20of%20Europe%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Sinaloa%20Cartel%20has%20a%20Twitter%20account%20with%20almost%20200%2C000%20followers%20and%20they%20tend%20to%20post%20nearly%20daily%2C%20engaging%20and%20posting%20images%20and%20other%20contents%20that%20glorify%20what%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20account%20has%20since%20been%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20greater%20attention%20to%20the%20role%20of%20online%20gaming%20in%20the%20drug%20trade%2C%20the%20Council%20of%20Europe's%20Pompidou%20Group%2C%20which%20works%20on%20international%20drug%20issues%2C%20held%20a%20forum%20in%20Mexico%20City%20on%20December%2019%20and%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnline%20games%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BGrand%20Theft%20Auto%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BWorld%20of%20Warcraft%26quot%3B%20provide%20perfect%20cover%20for%20cartels%20to%20discreetly%20sell%20drugs%20or%20find%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmoji%20conversations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20darknet%20has%20been%20decreasing%20in%20popularity%20for%20cartels%2C%20law%20enforcement%20has%20gotten%20pretty%20good%20at%20getting%20into%20the%20darknet%2C%20whereas%20video%20games%20garner%20really%20untapped%20resources%20and%20are%20very%20unmonitored%2C%26quot%3B%20Shultz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20online%20games%2C%20users%20can%20connect%20with%20almost%20anyone%2C%20teenagers%20can%20talk%20to%20strangers%2C%20and%20there%20are%20not%20many%20controls%2C%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20games'%20internal%20messaging%20systems%20are%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20intercept%2C%20particularly%20when%20traffickers%20communicate%20with%20emoticons%20or%20emojis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20entire%20conversation%20can%20be%20carried%20out%20with%20symbols%2C%20avoiding%20any%20suspect%20words%20that%20could%20trigger%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20drug%20circles%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20electric%20plug%20emoji%20means%20%26quot%3Bdealer%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20small%20palm%20tree%20means%20%26quot%3Bmarijuana%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20key%20stands%20for%20%26quot%3Bcocaine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexican%20police%20were%20the%20first%20to%20notice%20the%20practice%2C%20with%20an%20early%20case%20involving%20three%20adolescents%20aged%2011%20to%2014%20who%20were%20recruited%20while%20playing%20%26quot%3BGarena%20Free%20Fire%26quot%3B%20and%20offered%20%24200%20a%20week%20to%20be%20lookouts%20in%20Mexico%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20were%20arrested%20just%20before%20boarding%20a%20bus%20that%20their%20recruiter%20had%20bought%20them%20tickets%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20an%20isolated%20phenomenon'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20type%20of%20transaction%20and%20dealing%20is%20still%20much%20more%20common%20on%20Instagram%20or%20Snapchat%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20cases%20with%20video%20games%20have%20been%20localised%20near%20the%20US-Mexico%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Shultz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Europe%20video%20games%20are%20very%20unregulated%2C%20they're%20not%20monitored%20so%20this%20could%20be%20very%20well%20percolating%20under%20the%20surface%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThomas%20Kattau%2C%20deputy%20executive%20secretary%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Europe's%20Pompidou%20Group%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20a%20global%20issue%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20is%20you%20need%20to%20have%20a%20forum%20where%20we%20can%20make%20law%20enforcement%20and%20governments%20aware%20of%20the%20phenomenon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMexico%20is%20the%20country%20that%20has%20taken%20the%20lead%20on%20this%20issue%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20law%20enforcement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20we%20have%20seen%20similar%20things%20occurring%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20other%20countries%2C%20and%20therefore%20we%20see%20it%20is%20not%20an%20anecdotal%2C%20isolated%20phenomenon%2C%20but%20something%20which%20is%20quickly%20replicating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShultz%20and%20Kattau%20suggest%20better%20education%20both%20for%20parents%20and%20their%20children%20about%20the%20risks%20of%20online%20games%2C%20as%20well%20as%20greater%20efforts%20by%20game%20developers%20to%20reinforce%20protections%2C%20above%20all%20by%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20improve%20surveillance%20software.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703053920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2Fvjrmnguo_gaming-generic_625x300_25_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkey-emoji-means-cocaine-how-drugs-are-sold-in-online-gaming-chatrooms-4708110%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Narcotics%20police%20the%20world%20over%20are%20sprucing%20up%20their%20video%20game%20skills%2C%20as%20cartels%20go%20increasingly%20online%20to%20sell%20drugs%20and%20recruit%20dealers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkey-emoji-means-cocaine-how-drugs-are-sold-in-online-gaming-chatrooms-4708110%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkey-emoji-means-cocaine-how-drugs-are-sold-in-online-gaming-chatrooms-4708110%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkey-emoji-means-cocaine-how-drugs-are-sold-in-online-gaming-chatrooms-4708110%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kristen%2C%20Katy%20in%20'Love%20Lies%20Bleeding'%20trailer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703053832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-10