o%20hand%20out%20with%20my%20little%20boy%20for%20Christmas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Micucci%20underwent%20the%20surgery%20last%20Friday.%20She%20posted%20a%20video%20at%20that%20time%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%20everybody%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20TikTok%2C%20it's%20a%20'Sick%20Tok.'%20I'm%20in%20the%20hospital%20but%20it's%20because%20I%20had%20lung%20cancer%20surgery%20yesterday.%26quot%3B%20She%20stated%20that%20the%20diagnosis%20was%20a%20surprise%20as%20she%20had%20not%20even%20smoked%20a%20cigarette%20in%20her%20life.%20%26quot%3BThey%20caught%20it%20early.%20It's%20pretty%20weird%20because%20I've%20never%20smoked%20a%20cigarette%20in%20my%20life.%20So%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it%20was%20a%20surprise%2C%20but%20also%2C%20I%20guess%20it%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20one%20thing%20in%20my%20bloodwork%20that%20came%20back%20really%20high%20...%20It%20was%20HCRP%20...%20not%20sure%20what%20that%20is%20exactly%20but%20I%20guess%20it%20means%20there%20is%20inflammation%20somewhere.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20a%20preventative%20doc%20who%20did%20a%20few%20scans.%20He%20scanned%20my%20heart%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20spot%20in%20my%20lung%20was%20noticed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained%20on%20how%20she%20found%20out%20about%20the%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Ms%20Micucci%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Bang%20Theory%26quot%3B%20for%20three%20seasons%20as%20the%20shy%20and%20awkward%20Lucy%2C%20a%20woman%20that%20Raj%20meets%20at%20a%20party.%20She%20has%20also%20appeared%20in%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Met%20Your%20Mother%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BWeeds%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPsych%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703052120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbc36e6q8_kate-big-bang-theory_625x300_20_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwent-great-the-big-bang-theory-actor-ka