get%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20masterpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiugiaro%2C%20who%20designed%20the%20cult%20classic%20DeLorean%2C%20called%20the%20Cybertruck%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Picasso%20of%20automobiles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delorean%20designer%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feurope.autonews.com%2Fcars-concepts%2Fdesigner-giorgetto-giugiaro-thinks-teslas-cybertruck-picasso%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeaking%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20an%20Italian%20newspaper%20la%20Repubblica%2C%20where%20he%20gushed%20about%20the%20Cybertruck.%20Giugiaro%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20vehicle%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20successful%20because%20people%20want%20to%20stand%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20Cybertruck%20is%20notable%20for%20being%20the%20first%20stainless%20steel%20vehicle%20to%20be%20produced%20since%20Giugiaro's%20DeLorean.%20The%20DeLorean%2C%20which%20appeared%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BBack%20to%20the%20Future%26quot%3B%20film%20series%2C%20was%20launched%20in%20the%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20represent%20the%20search%20for%20harmony%20and%20perfection%20but%20for%20emotion%20and%20robustness%2C%26quot%3B%20Giugiaro%20said%20of%20the%20Cybertruck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time%20Giugiaro%20has%20heaped%20praise%20on%20the%20Cybertruck.%20He%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F11%2F14%2F1212575764%2Ftesla-cybertruck-design-delorean-designer-giorgetto-giugiaro-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20month%20that%20the%20truck%20would%20be%20a%20hit%20with%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20wants%20to%20distinguish%20themselves.%20It's%20a%20market%20necessity%2C%20and%20the%20Cybertruck%20will%20surely%20be%20successful%2C%20I'm%20sure%20of%20it.%20I'm%20convinced%20it%20will%20find%20its%20admirers%2C%26quot%3B%20Giugiaro%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vote%20of%20confidence%20from%20Giugiaro%20would%20probably%20make%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20very%20happy.%20Giugiaro's%20DeLorean%20was%20one%20of%20the%20vehicles%20that%20inspired%20the%20Cybertruck's%20design%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearly-tesla-cybertruck-design-ideas-inspiration-curves-elon-musk-photo-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalter%20Isaacson's%20biography%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20has%20big%20plans%20for%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20if%20his%20latest%20posts%20on%20X%20are%20any%20indication.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Musk%20said%20Tesla%20would%20be%20rolling%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bmod%20package%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20allow%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-you-can-use-cybertruck-as-a-boat-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%20to%20function%20as%20a%20boat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20offer%20a%20mod%20package%20that%20enables%20Cybertruck%20to%20traverse%20at%20least%20100m%20of%20water%20as%20a%20boat%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1736943517115482218%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BMostly%20just%20need%20to%20upgrade%20cabin%20door%20seals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Tesla%20and%20Giugiaro%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelorean-designer-calls-cybertruck-the-picasso-of-automobiles-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17030428610