%20hostile%20air-superiority%20jets%20and%20improve%20the%20survivability%20of%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%20But%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20are%20much%20better%20than%20Russia%20at%20leveraging%20air%20power%2C%20using%20long-range%20reconnaissance%20and%20strikes%2C%20stealth%20aircraft%2C%20and%20advanced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-air-force-lacks-jets-to-destroy-ukraines-air-defenses-2023-11%5C%22%3Esuppression-of-enemy-air-defense%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoblin%20said%20that%20in%20air-to-air%20operations%2C%20Iranian%20pilots%20would%20likely%20face%20problems%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20%26quot%3BUkrainian%20pilots%20who%20find%20they%20can't%20press%20home%20attacks%20due%20to%20being%20outranged%20by%20enemy%20fire-and-forget%20beyond-visual-range%20missiles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20I'd%20guess%20American%20and%20Israeli%20pilots%20may%20more%20aggressively%20close%20with%20enemy%20air%20assets%20than%20Russian%20ones%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESu-35%20%E2%80%94%20no%20game-changer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iran%20F-5%20fighter%20jet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581abe4a79e5746976ade5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Iranian%20F-5%20fighter%20jet%20lands%20in%20Chabahar%20city%20in%20June%202009.%3Cp%3EEBRAHIM%20NOROUZI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBohl%20and%20Roblin%20both%20expect%20the%20eventual%20delivery%20of%20Su-35s%20to%20have%20limited%20impact%20on%20Iran's%20overall%20airpower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBohl%20said%20the%20jets%20%26quot%3Bwould%20ease%20some%20of%20Iran's%20defense%20problems%20by%20providing%20it%20with%20at%20least%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20advanced%20aircraft%20that%20might%20be%20helpful%20in%20deterring%20a%20limited%20air%20campaign.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETehran%20may%20treat%20the%20jets%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20like%20prestige%20prize%26quot%3B%20and%20be%20reluctant%20to%20use%20them%2C%20in%20which%20case%20they%20may%20be%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20a%20diplomatic%20and%20political%20win%20rather%20than%20a%20defense%20breakthrough%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20may%20also%20try%20to%20use%20its%20Su-35s%20%26quot%3Bcautiously%20as%20a%20backfield%20airborne%20early-warning%20plane%2C%20much%20like%20it%20used%20the%20F-14's%20AWG-9%20radar%20during%20the%20Iran-Iraq%20War%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shephard%20analysis%20notes%20that%20in%20a%20conflict%20with%20local%20rivals%2C%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Iran's%20aircraft%20and%20aircrews%2C%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iiss.org%2Fonline-analysis%2Fmilitary-balance%2F2023%2F11%2Ffar-from-museum-pieces-iranian-missile-munition-and-uav-ambition-on-display%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair-defense%20and%20land-attack%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20proximity%20of%20the%20combat%20zones%2C%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20bring%20its%20navy%20to%20bear%20may%20benefit%20Iranian%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iran%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20missile%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581ad681c5c7b8c9a099f4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221345%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIslamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20personnel%20next%20to%20a%20Majid%20anti-aircraft%20missile%20system%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20Tehran%20in%20November.%3Cp%3EMorteza%20Nikoubazl%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAgainst%20better-armed%20and%20better-trained%20US%20and%20Israeli%20forces%2C%20however%2C%20Iran%20would%20face%20myriad%20disadvantages%20even%20%3Cem%3Eif%20it%20had%3C%2Fem%3E%20Su-35s.%20The%20US%20and%20Israeli%20air%20forces%20have%20extensive%20advantages%20in%20training%20and%20support%20assets%2C%20Roblin%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Su-35's%20Irbis-E%20radar%20isn't%20a%20stealthy%20active%20electronically%20scanned%20array%20radar%20like%20those%20typically%20found%20on%20newer%20American%20and%20Israeli%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Irbis-E%20%26quot%3Bbasically%20lights%20up%20the%20aircraft%20to%20all%20observers%20in%20the%20neighborhood%26quot%3B%20when%20used%20at%20full%20power%2C%20Roblin%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20US%20or%20Israel%20would%20likely%20%26quot%3Bgo%20out%20of%20their%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20destroy%20Iranian%20Su-35s%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20it's%20not%20clear%20if%20Iran%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-targeting-cant-catch-ukraine-air-force-top-us-general-2023-9%5C%22%3Edodge%20those%20strikes%20as%20well%20as%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Su-35%20is%20a%20first%20step%20to%20modernizing%20Iran's%20air%20force%2C%20the%2024%20that%20Tehran%20is%20reportedly%20receiving%20will%20only%20be%20a%20limited%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20Iran's%20economic%20circumstances%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20even%20more%204.5-generation%20jets%20would%20likely%20be%20exorbitant%2C%20and%20the%20huge%20sums%20could%20be%20spent%20on%20military%20capabilities%20with%20a%20better-guaranteed%20bang%20for%20the%20buck%2C%20like%20ground-based%20air%20defenses%2C%20drones%2C%20or%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%20%26quot%3BIran's%20air%20force%20and%20its%20tentative%20modernization%20look%20more%20useful%2C%20though%2C%20if%20considered%20as%20a%20defense%20against%20less%20capable%20regional%20enemies%20or%20even%20internal%20uprisings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%20data-track-content%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-post-type%3D%5C%22post%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Iddon%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20and%20columnist%20w